{
  "stem": "11593.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the bullet went off, and the guy was killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it turn out to be that it was an accident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And apparently, the engineer [? grab it ?] and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took it all as an accident, and nothing happened to my dad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the guy was-- it was an accident.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got-- and he-- and he was dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I don't know how it happened, what had happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It just-- that incident happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During the occupation, some of the refugees that ran away from Prague and Vienna couldn't take it anymore, and some committed suicide, especially when one day, a young girl-- she was the daughter of the manager of the cement factory, a beautiful girl about 17 or 18 years old-- your name was Hannah Prusak, P-R-U-S-A-K-- was raped and shot in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Apparently, she was raped by Ukrainian militiamen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but then Hungarian-- the Germans officers found out who the militiamen were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they beat them up so badly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then it was blamed on the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they came to Schleifstein, the head of the Judenrat, and asked him to give them 10 hostages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took 10 older Jews, and they killed them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Another incident I remember, there was a carpenter, a nice carpenter by the name of [POLISH] that the Todt Organisation want him to work for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Aung one work for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To resolve the problem, they took him in the street, and they hung him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One-- no, this was a Jewish carpenter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That the Todt Organisation want him to work for the Todt Organisation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Aung wanted him for the Aung Organisation.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
